ISLAMABAD, May 25 (APP): Chief Minister Punjab Sardar Usman Buzdar, Chief Minister Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Mahmood Khan and Chief Minister Gilgit Baltistan Khalid Khursheed Tuesday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan.
During the meeting, overall situation in the provinces and development issues came under discussion.
